S.FORM: El Salvador Gaga kska Kska Hunac Meycow ka El salvador, 13 50 N, 88 55 W ka gaga na nniqan. Kana ka knlbangan na o 21,041 sq km(hangan na o Tg153)(knlbanga dxgal o 20,721 sq km, knlbangan qsiya o 320 sq km). Kana ka sejiqun o niqan 6,156,670 hiyi. Gaga San Salvador ka pusu alang paru, jiyax 15 idas 9 ka jiyax skrayan klwaan. Manu ka dxgal El salvador ga wada sugan 74.7 ka dxgal qpahan, 13.60 ka dxgal bbuyu, rahuq dxgal do niqan 11.70 na. Bukung klwaan ta sayang o kiya ka Salvador Sánchez Cerén, pnaah hngkawas2014 idas 6 jiyax 1pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.
